      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "直觉会说：两点之间直线最短，那自然最快。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
