      "size": 23328,
      "text": "据说牛顿收到问题，当晚就给出了答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "problem",
      "line_id": "prob-3",
      "filename": "problem-prob-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/xiaoxiao/problem-prob-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "这道题催生了一门全新的数学分支——变分法。"
